PSXDataSelector.nativeStatement: SELECT RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTID, RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTNAME FROM RXSLOTTYPE WHERE RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTID NOT IN (SELECT RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTID FROM RXVARIANTSLOTTYPE,RXSLOTTYPE WHERE RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTTYPE=1 or ( RXVARIANTSLOTTYPE.SLOTID =RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTID AND RXVARIANTSLOTTYPE.VARIANTID=:"PSXParam/variantid"))
SELECT SITENAME, SITEID FROM RXSITES WHERE SITEID NOT IN (SELECT SITEID FROM PSX_VARIANT_SITE WHERE VARIANTID = :"PSXParam/variantid")
